ely participate in outdoor adventure activities. We have meticulously designed varied itineraries that allow you to explore the country\'s vast cultural repository, visit the historical cities and monuments, and take a delight in our comprehensive adventure offerings.\";s:21:\"adventures_main_title\";s:30:\"Check out our Active Adventure\";s:14:\"trekking_title\";s:15:\"Trekking/Hiking\";s:18:\"trekking_sub_title\";s:0:\"\";s:20:\"trekking_description\";s:178:\"Trekking in Nepal is one of the popular tourism activities in Nepal. Nepal trekking is one of the best way of experiencing the natural beauty and rich cultural heritage of Nepal.\";s:13:\"trekking_link\";s:44:\"http://highhimalayatreks.com/nepal-trekking/\";s:19:\"peak_climbing_title\";s:13:\"Peak Climbing\";s:23:\"peak_climbing_sub_title\";s:0:\"\";s:25:\"peak_climbing_description\";s:213:\"In Nepal, there are some small peaks below 6,500 meters that can be combined with organized trekking tour. These peaks lie close to popular and accessible trekking routes in Everest, Annapurna, and Langtang region\";s:18:\"peak_climbing_link\";s:1:\"#\";s:17:\"mountaining_title\";s:11:\"Mountaining\";s:21:\"mountaining_sub_title\";s:0:\"\";s:23:\"mountaining_description\";s:223:\"Mountaineering in Nepal is one of the prime adventure activities. Nepal Himalaya stretches (800 km) from east to west encompassing the world’s eight highest peaks that rise above (8,000 m) including Mt. Everest (8,848 m).\";s:16:\"mountaining_link\";s:1:\"#\";s:19:\"nature_safari_title\";s:23:\"Nature Tours and Safari\";s:23:\"nature_safari_sub_title\";s:0:\"\";s:25:\"nature_safari_description\";s:230:\"Nature tours and wildlife safari in Nepal immerse you in the great outdoors and stay in the heart of nature. You will enjoy a host of expert-led activities and explorations, without  compromising to  style, quality and facilities.\";s:18:\"nature_safari_link\";s:1:\"#\";s:19:\"river_rafting_title\";s:13:\"River Rafting\";s:23:\"river_rafting_sub_title\";s:0:\"\";s:25:\"river_rafting_description\";s:261:\"The beautiful Himalayan ranges provide an incredible variety of unmatched whitewater challenges for both rafters and kayakers. No other country in the world has such a choice of trips on wild rivers with warm water, a subtropical climate and white sand beaches \";s:18:\"river_rafting_link\";s:1:\"#\";s:26:\"culture_and_heritage_title\";s:0:\"\";s:31:\"culture_and_heritage__sub_title\";s:0:\"\";s:32:\"culture_and_heritage_description\";s:0:\"\";s:25:\"culture_and_heritage_link\";s:0:\"\";s:22:\"exclusive_offers_title\";s:25:\"Exclusive offers for 2019\";s:28:\"exclusive_offers_description\";s:38:\"Vivamus molestie gravida turpis offers\";s:18:\"meet_experts_title\";s:28:\"Meet your expert local guide\";s:24:\"meet_experts_description\";s:571:\"<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aenean rutrum nulla id ante consectetur sagittis. Vivamus semper lorem quis viverra consequat. Nulla facilisi. Curabitur nec mauris mollis, congue lorem sed, porta dolor. Nunc scelerisque massa lectus, tristique molestie ante gravida eget.</p>\r\n<p>Vestibulum ullamcorper, odio vitae ornare tempus, nunc arcu ornare nunc, vitae eleifend quam neque ac lectus. Nam et massa sit amet justo tincidunt lobortis. Proin vel luctus erat, in semper velit. Donec congue viverra consequat.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\";s:18:\"meet_experts_video\";s:123:\"<iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/kBeOTmPseII\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\";s:20:\"mission_vision_title\";s:30:\"Our Vision, Mission and Values\";s:26:\"mission_vision_description\";s:1396:\"<div class=\"desc\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<p><strong>Mission</strong></p>\r\n<p>We want to be leader  in the  tourism  industry in Nepal  through innovative service management and the range of travel related products . We want to  sustain a reputation of quality through excellent service, customer care, and a friendly, professional staff. Our guests are always the focus of our company. We want to  generate a profit in an ethical manner while meeting and exceeding our clients\' expectations.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Vision</strong></p>\r\n<p>Our vision is to invest profits back into our isolated communities who are out of reach from the  mainstream of  national development .We want to create more employment  opportunities for the  youths in the socially and economically backward communities.  Our growth means more investment in communities and a broader reach into more communities. This is why we send travelers on unforgettable, community-focused adventure trips to empower  underprivileged locals.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Values</strong></p>\r\n<p>Our clients are an extension of our own families and we do every effort for  their comfort, safety and happiness. We have earned reputation amongst the clients due to our many years of experience in tourism that brings clients  back year after year and are passionate about providing a fun and exciting travel experience.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\";s:18:\"testimonials_title\";s:16:\"Vivamus molestie\";s:24:\"testimonials_description\";s:38:\"Vivamus molestie gravida turpis offers\";s:17:\"why_us_main_title\";s:23:\"Why High Mountain Treks\";s:14:\"why_us_1_title\";s:12:\"Expert Guide\";s:18:\"why_us_1_sub_title\";s:32:\"Vestibulum auctor dapibus neque.\";s:13:\"why_us_1_link\";s:1:\"#\";s:14:\"why_us_2_title\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"why_us_2_sub_title\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"why_us_2_link\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"why_us_3_title\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"why_us_3_sub_title\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"why_us_3_link\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"why_us_4_title\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"why_us_4_sub_title\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"why_us_4_link\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"why_us_5_title\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"why_us_5_sub_title\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"why_us_5_link\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"why_us_6_title\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"why_us_6_sub_title\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"why_us_6_link\";s:0:\"\";s:19:\"special_tours_title\";s:4:\"Test\";s:25:\"special_tou