(1918, 182, 'trip_itinerary', '<strong>Day 01:</strong> Arrival Kathmandu and transfer to hotel\r\n<strong>Day 02:</strong> Fly Kathmandu to Lukla (2,840 m) (39 min) and trek Lukla to Phakdingma (2,610 m) overnight at lodge\r\n<strong>Day 03:</strong> Trek to Namche Bazaar (3,340 m) approx 6 hrs overnight at lodge\r\n<strong>Day 04:</strong> Rest &amp; acclimatization day in Namche Bazaar you will excursion to walk full day around Syangboche, Everest view hotel, Khumjung village &amp; back to Namche Bazaar (3,340 m) overnight at lodge\r\n<strong>Day 05:</strong> Trek to Thame ((3,821 m) approx 3 hrs overnight at lodge\r\n<strong>Day 06:</strong> Trek to Lungden (4,369 m) approx 4 hrs overnight at lodge\r\n<strong>Day 07:</strong> Trek to Gokyo (4790 m) via Cross over Renjo La Pass (5,369 m) approx 8/9 hrs overnight at lodge\r\n<strong>Day 08:</strong> You will climb Gokyo Ri (5,369 m) and after lunch trek to Gyazumba Lake (Five Lake) (4,990 m) &amp; back to Gokyo (4,790 m) approx 8-9 hrs walk overnight at lodge\r\n<strong>Day 09:</strong> Trek to Thagnag (4,700 m) approx 2 hours and taking rest at Thagnag overnight at lodge\r\n<strong>Day 10:</strong> Trek Thagnag to cross over Chola Pass (5,420 m) and trek to Dzongla (4,830 m) approx 7/8 hrs overnight at lodge\r\n<strong>Day 11:</strong> Trek to Lobuche (4,910 m) approx 3 hrs overnight at lodge\r\n<strong>Day 12:</strong> Trek to Gorakshep (5,140 m) after Lunch trek to Everest Base Camp at (5,364 m) 2 hours each way) &amp; back to Gorakshep approx 7 hrs overnight at lodge<strong>\r\nDay 13:</strong> From Gorakshep climb Kala Pattar (5,545 m) &amp; you will back walk down to Dingboche (4,410 m) approx 6/7 hrs overnight at lodge\r\n<strong>Day 14:</strong> Trek to Tengboche (3,860 m) approx 4 hrs overnight at lodge\r\n<strong>Day 15:</strong> Trek to Namche Bazaar (3,340 m) approx 5 hrs overnight at lodge\r\n<strong>Day 16:</strong> Trek to Lukla (2,840 m) approx 6/7 hrs overnight at lodge\r\n<strong>Day 17:</strong> Fly back Lukla to Kathmandu (39 min) and transfer to hotel\r\n<strong>Day 18:</strong> Free day in Kathmandu for rest and shopping\r\n<strong>Day 19:</strong> Transfer to international airport for your final departure (Trip ends.)'),
