(6105, 393, 'trip_itinerary', '<strong>Day 01: </strong>Arrival and transfer to hotel\r\n\r\n<strong>Day02:  </strong>Drive to Jalbire (1000m.)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 03:</strong> Trek to Chanaute (1350m, 4hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 04:</strong> Trek to Khani Gaon (2000m, 6hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 05:</strong> Rest day with Local Village sightseeing\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 06:</strong> Trek to Forest Camp (3150m, 6-7 hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 07:</strong> Trek to Pati (3765m, 5 hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 08:</strong> Trek to Bhairav Kund (4250m, 3 hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 09:</strong> Trek to Sherpa Gaon (2500m, 6 hrs) &amp; enjoy Sunset view\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 10:</strong> Trek to Larcha (1500m.) and visit Hot spring (Kodari highway)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 11:</strong> Drive to Kathmandu\r\n\r\n<strong>Day12:</strong>  Kathmandu sightseeing and shopping\r\n\r\n<strong>Day13:</strong> Transfer to the Airport for final departure'),
