(13655, 871, 'trip_itinerary', '<strong>Day 01:</strong> Arrival in Kathmandu &amp; transfer to hotel\r\n<strong>Day 02-03:</strong> Official works for expedition and briefing by officer in the Ministry of Tourism.\r\n<strong>Day 04: </strong>Drive to Beni\r\n<strong>Day 05: </strong>Beni to Tatopani (1,189 m).\r\n<strong>Day 06: </strong>Tatopani to Ghasa (2,012 m).\r\n<strong>Day 07: </strong>Ghasa to Tukuche (2,591 m).\r\n<strong>Day 08:</strong> Tukuche to Marpha (2,667 m).\r\n<strong>Day 09:</strong> Marpha to Yak Kharka (3680m)\r\n<strong>Day 10: </strong>Yak Kharka to French Col\r\n<strong>Day 11: </strong>French Col to Dhalulagiri Base Camp (4700m)\r\n<strong>Day 12-43: </strong>Climbing period &amp; summit\r\n<strong>Day 44:</strong> Cleaning up Base Camp and trek to Yak Kharka\r\n<strong>Day 45:</strong> Yak Kharka to Jomsom (2750m)\r\n<strong>Day 46:</strong> Fly Jomsom to Pokhara and relax\r\n<strong>Day 47:</strong> Drive to Kathmandu\r\n<strong>Day 48:</strong> Free day in Kathmandu\r\n<strong>Day 49:</strong> Last minute, transfers to airport for your onward journey.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
