(16462, 1020, 'trip_itinerary', '<strong>Day 01</strong>:Arrive Kathmandu, transfer to hotel / tour briefing\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 02</strong>:Sightseeing tour of Kathmandu Valley &amp; permits preparation\r\n<strong>Day 03:</strong> Fly Nepalgunj to Jumla (2370m\r\n<strong>Day 04:</strong> Jumla to Danphe Lagna (3500m)\r\n<strong>Day 05:</strong> Danphe Lagna to Chautha (2770m)\r\n<strong>Day 06:</strong> Chauta to Dhotu (2380m)\r\n<strong>Day 07:</strong>  Dhotu to Rara Lake (2980m)\r\n<strong>Day 08:</strong> Acclimatization in Rara Lake\r\n<strong>Day 09:</strong> Rara Lake to Gorosingha (3190m)\r\n<strong>Day10:</strong> Gorosingha to Sinja (2440m)\r\n<strong>Day 11:</strong> Sinja to Jaljala Chaur (3270m)\r\n<strong>Day 12:</strong> Jaljal Chaur to Jumla (2370m)\r\n<strong>Day 13:</strong> Fly Jumla to Nepalgunj &amp; same day fly to Kathmandu\r\n<strong>Day 14:</strong> Free day in Kathmandu\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 15:</strong> Transfer to the Airport for your onward destination.'),
