(16787, 1030, 'trip_itinerary', '<strong>Day 01:</strong>Arrival and transfer to hotel\r\n<strong>Day02:</strong>  Drive from Kathmandu to Beni (810m) (10hrs)\r\n<strong>Day03:</strong>Trek from Beni to Babichoaur (950m, 5hrs)\r\n<strong>Day04: </strong> Trek from Babiachaur to Dharapani 6hrs\r\n<strong>Day05: </strong> Trek to Muri 7hrs\r\n<strong>Day06:</strong>Trek to Baghar (2080m)\r\n<strong>Day07: </strong> Trek to Dobang (2520m, 5hrs)\r\n<strong>Day08: </strong>Trek to Sallaghari (3110m, 6hrs)\r\n<strong>Day09:</strong>  Trek to Upper Vungini/ Italian Base Camp (3660m, 6hrs)\r\n<strong>Day10:</strong> Trek to Glacier Camp /French Camp (4940m, 4hrs)\r\n<strong>Day11: </strong>Trek to Dhaulagiri Base Camp (4740m, 5hrs)\r\n<strong>Day12:</strong>  Trek to French Col (5010m) or Hidden Valley (5200m, 4hrs)\r\n<strong>Day13:</strong>Trek to Yak Kharka (7hrs)\r\n<strong>Day14:</strong> Trek to Marpha (2670m, 5hrs)\r\n<strong>Day15:</strong> Trek to Ghasa (6hrs)\r\n<strong>Day16:</strong>Trek to Tatopani (1189m, 5hrs)\r\n<strong>Day17:</strong> Trek to Ghorepani (2853m, 7hrs)\r\n<strong>Day18:</strong> Trek to Tadapani.\r\n<strong>Day19:</strong>Trek to Ghandruk (1950m)\r\n<strong>Day20:</strong> Trek to Pothana (1990m,6 hrs)\r\n<strong>Day21:</strong>Trek to Dhampus Phedi (113m, 4hrs) &amp; drive to Pokhara\r\n<strong>Day22:</strong>Free day in Pokhara\r\n<strong>Day23:</strong> Drive from Pokhara to Kathmandu (7 hrs)\r\n<strong>Day24: </strong> Kathmandu sightseeing and shopping\r\n<strong>Day25:</strong> Transfer to the Airport for final departure'),
