(17531, 1038, 'trip_itinerary', '<strong>Day 01: </strong>Arrival Kathmandu and transfer to hotel\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 02: </strong>Kathmandu sightseeing &amp; permits preparation day\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 03:</strong> Fly to Lukla (2804 meters) &amp; trek to Phakding (2610 meters) 3 hours.\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 04:</strong> Trek to Namche Bazaar (3441 meters) 5.30 hours\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 05:</strong> Rest /acclimatization day in Namche Bazaar\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 06: </strong>Trek to Tengboche (3860 meters) 5 hours.\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 07:</strong> Trek to Dingboche (4350 meters) 5.30 hours.\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 08:</strong> Excursion to Chhukung (4710 meters) and trek back to Dingboche. 4.30 hours\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 09:</strong> Trek to Lobuche (4910 meters) 5 hours.\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 10:</strong> Trek to Everest Base Camp (5365 m) &amp; trek back to Gorak Shep (5180 m) 7 hrs.\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 11:</strong> Trek to Kalapattar (5555 m) then trek down to Lobuche (4930 meters) 6 hours\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 12:</strong> Trek to Lobuche Peak Base Camp (4950 meters). 5 hours\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 13:</strong> Summit to Lobuche East Peak (6119 meters) and back to Base Camp.\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 14:</strong> Spare day in case of bad weather.\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 15:</strong> Trek to Pangboche (4000 meters) 6 hours.\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 16:</strong> Trek to Namche Bazaar 6 hours.\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 17:</strong> Trek to Lukla 6 hours.\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 18:</strong> Fly back to Kathmandu\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 19:</strong> Free day for shopping or leisure\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 20:</strong> Airport transfer for final departure.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
