(19286, 1061, 'trip_itinerary', '<strong>Day 01:</strong> Arrival in Kathmandu &amp; transfer to hotel.\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 02:</strong> Arrangements of necessary permits for the trek\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 03:</strong> Drive Kathmandu to Shivalaya (1790 m, 9hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 04:</strong> Trek Shivalaya to Khahare (2175 m, 4hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 05:</strong> Trek Khahare to Panipakha (3105 m, 4hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 06:</strong> Trek Panipakha to Manedanda (3940 m, 3hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 07:</strong> Trek Manedanda to Panch Pokhari (4515 m, 4hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 08:</strong> Trek Panch Pokhari to Tare (4140 m, 5 hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 09:</strong> Trek Tare to Ngeju (3690 m, 4hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 10:</strong> Trek Ngeju to Lhachhewar (2665 m, 4hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 11:</strong> Trek Lhachhewar to Kyama (2380 m, 5hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 12:</strong> Trek Kyama to Gumdel (2255 m, 3hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 13:</strong> Trek Gumdel to Serding\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 14:</strong> Trek Serding to Thodung to Lapchane (3105 m, 5hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 15:</strong> Trek Lapchane to Those (1755 m, 4hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 16:</strong> Drive from Those to Kathmandu (1350 m, 9hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 17:</strong> Kathmandu sightseeing\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 18:</strong> Final Departure'),
