ation in Kathmandu because of early return from the trekking (due to any reason)</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\">Tips &amp; Gratuities for trekking guide &amp; porter (s)</span></li>\r\n</ul>'),
