(20786, 1083, 'trip_itinerary', '<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\"><strong>Day 01: </strong>Arrive in Kathmandu and transfer to hotel, in the evening briefing about the trek/climbing</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\"><strong>Day 02:</strong><b> </b>Permits preparation and shopping day, overnight at hotel.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\"><strong>Day 03:</strong> Fly to Lukla (2840m.) (39mins)  and trek Lukla to Chutenga (3050m.) approx 3 hours</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\"><strong>Day 04:</strong> Trek Chutenga to Cross Chatra La Pass (4610m.) and trek to Chatra Buk (4119M.) approx 6 hours</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\"><strong>Day05:</strong> Trek Chatra Buk to Kothe (3789m.) approx 6 hours</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\"><strong>Day 06:</strong> Rest day for Acclimatization and excursion around Kothe cave and Stupa at Kothe (3789m.)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\"><strong>Day 07:</strong> Trek Kothe to Tangnag (4465m.) approx 5 hours</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\"><strong>Day 08:</strong> Trek Tangnag to Khare (5015m.) approx 5 hours</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\"><strong>Day 09:</strong> Trek Khare to Mera Peak High Camp (5800m.) approx 3 hours and Prayer Puja day for the Summit at Mera Peak High Camp</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\"><strong>Day 10:</strong> We keep 1 reserve day in case of bad weather situation at Khare or Mera Peak High Camp.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\"><strong>Day 11:</strong> High Camp Summit Mera Peak (6654m.) and back to Mera Peak High Camp trek to Khongma Dingma (4815m.) Full day we walk base camp.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\"><strong style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\">Day 12:</strong> Trek Khongma Dingma to Panch Pokhari (Five Lake) (5400m.) approx 5-6 hours   </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\"><strong>Day 13:</strong> A rest day. The Climbing guides and Climbing Sherpas ascend the Amphu Laptsa Pass to establish fixed lines and prepare the pass for tomorrow\'s crossing Camp.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\"><strong>Day 14:</strong> Cross Amphu Lapcha Pass (5700m.) We now descend fixed ropes to the Imja Glacier and Trek to Chhukung (4,730m.) approx full day  </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\"><strong>Day 15:</strong> Trek Chhukung to Tengboche (3860m.) approx 4-5 hours</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\"><strong>Day 16:</strong> Trek Tengboche to Namche Bazaar (3340m.) approx 5 hours</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\"><strong>Day 17:</strong> Trek Namche Bazaar to Lukla (2840m.) approx 6-7 hours</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\"><strong>Day 18:</strong> Fly back Lukla to Kathmandu (39mins) and transfer to hotel</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\"><strong>Day 19:</strong> Kathmandu City Sightseeing</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\"><strong>Day 20:</strong> Transfer to international airport for your final departure (Trip ends.)</span></p>'),
