(20850, 829, 'cost_includes', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Airport pick up and transfer to hotel</li>\r\n 	<li>Four nights hotel accommodation in Kathmandu with breakfast</li>\r\n 	<li>Trekking accommodation in trekkers lodge /Tea house or camp</li>\r\n 	<li>English speaking climbing guide</li>\r\n 	<li>Necessary porters to carry your baggage during the trekking.( Two persons get one trekking porter)</li>\r\n 	<li>Three time meals during the trekking- Breakfast, Lunch &amp; Dinner</li>\r\n 	<li>Sagarmatha National Park entry permit</li>\r\n 	<li>Trekker’s Information Management system (TIMS)</li>\r\n 	<li>Mera Peak climbing permit</li>\r\n 	<li>Insurance for Nepalese staff. (Trekking guide and porters)\r\nGuide and porter\'s salary, food, drinks, accommodations\r\nMedical supplies (first aid kit will be available).\r\nGovernment Tax and office service charge\r\nAirport drop at the time of departure</li>\r\n</ul>'),
