(21995, 1104, 'trip_itinerary', '<strong>Day 01: </strong>Arrival Kathmandu and transfer to hotel\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 02-03: </strong>Preparation day &amp; briefing about the trek/climb\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 04: </strong>Fly to Lukla (2,840 m) (39mins) and trek to Phakdingma (2,610 m) (3hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 05: </strong>Trek to Namche Bazaar (3,440 m) (5hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 06: </strong>Rest day in for acclimatization &amp; Excursion around Namche Bazaar/Khumjung (3,790 m)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 07: </strong>Trek to Thame (3,821 m/3hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 08: </strong>Trek to Lungden (4,369 m/4hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 09: </strong>Trek to Gokyo (4,790 m) via Renjo La Pass (5,369 m/9hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 10: </strong>Climb to Gokyo Ri (5,369 m) &amp; trek to Thangna (4,700 m) via Gokyo village (5hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 11: </strong>Trek to Lobuche (4,910 m) via Cho La pass (5,420 m) and Dzongla (4,830 m/9-10hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 12: </strong>Trek to Gorakshep to Everest Base Camp (5,364 m) &amp; back to Gorakshep (5,140 m/7hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 13: </strong>Climb to Kala Patthar (5,545 m) &amp; trek to continue Dingboche (4,410 m/7hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 14: </strong>Rest Day in Dingboche for acclimatization (4,410 m)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 15: </strong>Trek to Chhukung (4,730 m/2hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 16: </strong>Trek from Chhukung to Island Peak Base Camp (4,970 m/3-4hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 17: </strong>Summit day Island Peak (6,160 m) &amp; same day trek back  to Chhukung (4730 m)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 18: </strong>Trek to Pangboche (3,930 m/3-4hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 19: </strong>Rest day in Pangboche (3,930 m)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 20: </strong>Trek from Pangboche to Mt. Ama Dablam Base Camp (4,640 m/3hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 21: </strong>Trek to Advanced Base Camp (5,009 m)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 22: </strong>Trek Move to Camp 1 (5,400 m)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 23: </strong>Move to Camp 2 (5,800 m)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 24: </strong>Move to Camp 3 (6,400 m)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 25: </strong>Summit Day to Mt. Ama Dablam (6,812 m) &amp; Move to Camp 2 (5,700 m)\r\n\r\n<strong>Note: We keep 3 Reserved days in case for bad weather situation</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 26- 28: </strong>Reserve day\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 29: </strong>Move from Camp 2 (5,800 m) to Mt. Ama Dablam Base Camp, (4,640 m)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 30: </strong>Trek from Mt. Ama Dablam Base Camp to Tengboche (3,860 m/3hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 31: </strong>Trek to Namche Bazaar (3,440 m/4hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 32: </strong>Trek to Lukla (2,840 m/6hrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 33: </strong>Fly from Lukla to Kathmandu (39min)\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 34: </strong>Free day in Kathmandu and shopping\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 35: </strong>From hotel transfer to International Airport for your final departure (Trip ends)'),
