(141, 1, '2017-06-04 06:30:35', '2017-06-04 06:30:35', '<strong>Trekking in Nepal</strong> is one of the popular tourism activities in Nepal. Nepal trekking is one of the best way of experiencing the natural beauty and rich cultural heritage of Nepal. Nepal treks offers snow capped views of Nepal Himalaya, beautiful landscape, different ethnic groups &amp; their traditions, hospitality, lush valleys through forests of rhododendron, bamboo, oak, and hemlock, visiting one or two villages to next trekking destination. Nepal trekking is not simply walking hiking one day after another, it is rather a gradual way of experiencing of Nepal\'s diversity in terns of geography, people, religion and a wide range of culture. Nepal trekss can be a day hike to get to the top on a mountain or a ridge for the spectacular views of Himalayan peaks or it can be a hiking for a month passing through villages in the shadow of towering snow peaks, valleys, mountain pass experiencing rich culture, custom and the magnificent views of Himalayas in Nepal. The objective of Nepal trekking is not just the particular destination, but the journey itself. You travel at a modest pace, observing nature, rural communities, and spectacular mountain panoramas while you are trekking in Nepal Himalaya. Himalaya Journey Trekking experienced trekking guide will lead for path finding and an introduction to the local people, culture, religion and lifestyle.\r\n\r\nNepal has numerous trekking trails &amp; HJT operate all Nepal trekking destination such as Regular / Normal trekking trail, restricted trekking trail, non touristy trekking trail &amp; newly open trekking trail. All Nepal trekking destination haven’t lodge / tea house facilities so We Himalaya Journey Trekking and Expedition arrange camping / tented trekking &amp; Tea House / Lodge trekking as per trekkers wish. Nepal has numerous treks routes among them Everest trekking, Annapurna trekking &amp; Langtang trekking trail are most popular trekking destination in Nepal except that Kanchenjunga trekking ,Makalu base camp Trekking, Manaslu trekking, Mustang trekking, Upper Mustang trekking, Dolpo trekking, Upper Dolpa trekking, Rolwaling Trekking ,Kalinchowk trekking , Rolwaling Tashi lapcha pass trekking, Ganesh Himal trekking, Panch pokhari Trekking, Bhirab kunda trekking, Lo-Manthang trekking, Rara lake trekking, Tilaman pass trekking, Dudh kunda trekking, Pike Everest base camp trekking, Arun valley trekking, Timal Bholung trekking, Milke dada trekking, , Sailung trekking, , Tilicho lake pass/Meso kanto pass trekking, Narphu valley trekking, Around Dhaulagiri trekking also challenging and popular trekking trails in Nepal.\r\n\r\nObviously popular trekking trail such as in Annapurna region trekking : Annapurna circuit trekking, Annapurna jomsom Muktinath trekking, Annapurna, Ghorepani poon hill trekking, Annapurna base camp trekking, In Everest region trekking: such as Everest base camp trekking, Gokyo trekking, Gokyo cho la pass Everest base camp trekking, Everest view trekking and In Langtang region trekking : Langtang valley trekking, langtang Gosainkunda trekking, Langtang Helambu trekking, Around Katmandu valley trekking trails are most rewarded trekking in Nepal. Nepal trekking required trekking permit which trekkers obtain throughGovernment registered Nepal trekking Agency for the safety and secure trekking in Nepal Himalaya. Also for restricted trekking trail compulsion to use Nepal trekking company for obtain the special trekking permit. We Himalaya Journey Treks and Expedition arrange all trekking route of Nepal private or group join basis , Individual or groups, family and relatives, Friends &amp; different nationality trekkers with amazing life time experience of Nepal Himalaya! Treks in Nepal is amazing life time experience for those who love nature and mountains.', 'Nepal Trekking', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '18-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-06-04 06:30:35', '2017-06-04 06:30:35', '', 18, 'http://highhimalayatreks.com/18-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
