ith a long drive from Kathmandu to Arughat or <strong>Soti Khola</strong> and walk up to <strong>Mu Gompa</strong> (4000m). If you have time and add on visit <strong>Ganesh Himal Base Camp</strong> and Lungdang Nunnery Gompa, it will be a fantastic trekking. The trek ends at <strong>Arughat</strong> or Soti Khola and drive back to Kathmandu.', 'Tsum Valley Trekking', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tsum-valley-trekking', '', '', '2017-06-11 12:13:39', '2017-06-11 12:13:39', '', 18, 'http://highhimalayatreks.com/?page_id=538', 0, 'page', '', 0),
