(851, 1, '2018-11-27 12:25:31', '2018-11-27 12:25:31', 'Nepal is one of the best destinations for newly married couples. It is the land of colorful cultures, ancient history, and wilderness and has been popular getaway for honeymooners. Many couple makes their <strong>honeymoon trips</strong> <strong>to Nepal </strong>in the beginning of their conjugal life. It is not just an ordinary tour; rather it is a blend of leisure and a bit adventure suiting the couples\' interest and convenient time. Honeymoon is the most precious days for the newly married couples: it would be a time to relax, enjoy each other’s company and relieve memories of the special moments.\r\n\r\nYour first trip to Nepal as a married couple will be remarkable. Begin your life together in <strong>Kathmandu</strong>, one of the world’s most culturally rich city and sightseeing in different <strong>World Heritage Sites</strong> is an unforgettable experience.\r\n\r\nIt will be filled with fine food and fun times dictated by nothing. You will be travelling various places you’ve never heard of and showing you things you could have never imagined. Your travel will be as romantic and as boundless as your love for each other, which means your honeymoon trip can only be experienced in <strong>Himalayan country of Nepal</strong>.\r\n\r\n<strong>Nepal Honeymoon tour</strong> is especially designed, stay at one of Nepal\'s most legendary hotels, unique itineraries covering all popular places and flawless travel arrangements', 'Nepal Honeymoon Tour', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'nepal-honeymoon-tour', '', '', '2019-01-03 09:23:57', '2019-01-03 09:23:57', '', 24, 'http://highhimalayatreks.com/demo/?page_id=851', 0, 'page', '', 0),
