che and down to Lukla. From Lukla you will fly back to Kathmandu next day.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\">Amphu Laptsa Pass trekking is a very high altitude trek through glaciated valleys and only strong, well equipped, groups can attempt this route. <b>High Mountain Himalaya Treks and Expedition</b> will provide unrivalled service, plenty of rope and anchors with full mountaineering equipment, hygienic food, reliable trekking crew and an experienced climbing guide to ensure that Mera Peak Climbing and Amphu Lapcha Pass trekking will be an excellent adventure experience in Nepal.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"xmsonormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Tahoma\',sans-serif; color: #212121;\">After getting back to Kathmandu we will host a traditional Nepali dinner with ethnic cultural show.</span></p>', 'Mera Peak Climbing, via Amphu Laptsa Pass', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '829-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-01-13 13:57:35', '2019-01-13 13:57:35', '', 829, 'http://highhimalayatreks.com/demo/829-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
